description: Deletes the specified tags from a file system. If the DeleteTags request includes a tag key that doesn't exist, Amazon EFS ignores it and doesn't cause an error. For more information about tags and related restrictions, see Tag restrictions in the Billing and Cost Management User Guide. This operation requires permissions for the elasticfilesystem:DeleteTags action.

parameters.name: FileSystemId
parameters.description: The ID of the file system whose tags you want to delete (String).

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A list of tag keys to delete. (string) ---
